 @* ----- Form Fields ----- *@
                        </label> @* Closes the matching HTML element. *@
                    </div> @* Closes the matching HTML element. *@

 @* ----- Producer Display ----- *@
                    <div class="pw-vat-field" id="vatNumberGroup"> @* Starts a layout container for this section. *@
